name: Exact ODE condition
formula: $M\,dx + N\,dy = 0$ exact iff $\frac{\partial M}{\partial y} = \frac{\partial N}{\partial x}$
subject: Math

name: Stirling numbers (2nd kind)
formula: $S(n,k)$ = ways to partition $n$ into $k$ nonempty sets
subject: Math

name: Pigeonhole principle
formula: $n+1$ objects in $n$ boxes $\Rightarrow$ one box has $\geq 2$
subject: Math

name: Mann-Whitney U
formula: U statistic for two independent samples
subject: Statistics

name: Sign test
formula: Binomial test on signs of differences
subject: Statistics

name: Jordan normal form
formula: Every matrix similar to Jordan block form
subject: Math

name: Minimal polynomial
formula: Monic polynomial of least degree with m(A)=0
subject: Math

name: Squeeze theorem
formula: $a_n \leq b_n \leq c_n$ and $\lim a_n = \lim c_n = L \Rightarrow \lim b_n = L$
subject: Math

name: Rolle's theorem
formula: If f continuous on [a,b], differentiable on (a,b), f(a)=f(b), then exists c with f'(c)=0
subject: Math

name: Intermediate value theorem
formula: f continuous on [a,b], then f takes every value between f(a) and f(b)
subject: Math

name: First derivative test
formula: f'(c)=0 and f' changes sign at c then local extrema
subject: Math

name: Improper integral (type 2)
formula: $\int_a^b f = \lim_{t\to a^+} \int_t^b f$ if f unbounded at a
subject: Math

name: Comparison test (series)
formula: 0 ≤ a_n ≤ b_n, Σb_n converges ⇒ Σa_n converges
subject: Math

name: Integral test
formula: f positive, decreasing, then Σf(n) and ∫f dx same convergence
subject: Math

name: Percentile (definition)
formula: Value below which p% of data fall
subject: Statistics

name: Agresti-Coull interval
formula: Add 2 successes and 2 failures then Wald interval
subject: Statistics
